sentences: Aminata Savadogo (born 9 January 1993), occasionally known as simply Aminata, is a Latvian singer, songwriter, record producer, and model.
She represented Latvia in the Eurovision Song Contest 2015 with the song "Love Injected".
She released her debut studio album, Inner Voice, in April 2015.
